I truly believe in the Power of Each Individual, in the fact that it is the Individual who submits to <i>other powers</i>, rather than a power, or powers that <i>overtake</i> the Individual.</div><div><br /></div><div>So, and in direct dependency with the above, this is about the Individual, and about how these issues eventually make it more difficult for the one who has chosen to express his Power to do so, and consequently about how it slows us all down.</div><div><br /></div><div>The one who chooses, has chosen to express his Power understands that:</div><div><ul style="text-align: left;"><li>Privacy, Secrecy and everything that comes with those are hindrances to his/her development. As Mr Carl Gustav J\xc3\xbcng puts it:</li></ul><blockquote>"A secret acts like a poison that alienates his(her) beholder from the rest of the community"</blockquote><ul style="text-align: left;"><li>Thus Transparency, meaning not having anything to hide, anything at all, this meant <i>literally</i>, helps her/him by moving out a lot of the <i>blockages</i> that slows down the so much more powerful processor that her/his mind is</li><li>And Polarity, Separation, Division once he/she sees them as the Illusion they are, once he/she sees that we are (at the least) all striving for our self-accomplishment, each and every one of us, are to also be moved out of the way, for some or the rest of the blockages to be overcome</li></ul><div>So from there, the one who chooses, has chosen to express his Power focuses on bringing openness, freedom, sharing, <i>commonness</i> forth, and lets those who have not made that choice focus on what they wish to focus on.&nbsp;</div><div><br /></div><div>For the one who chooses, has chosen to express his Power knows that any other one who has made this choice will find the way to reach out. Whatever the state of the World that we live in. However high the walls are standing. However deep the traps are going.</div><div><br /></div><div>So let\'s redefine:</d