ess stress), even getting to know new people, and maybe, if there are enough people car-pooling, saving time (less traffic)...<br /><br />That\'s what car-pooling.be is about: providing you with a way to find people to car pool with. With the hope that after a few months you will have a list of 10, 15, 20 people to car pool with.<br /><br />Car-pooling.be provides the tool. And lets you and your fellow car-poolers see how you do it together. Ideally you\'ll be car-pooling in turns: for example four car-poolers with four cars would take turns, each one driving one day out of four, so you would not have to split cost and all... but it\'s up to you, so if it\'s easier to split cost for every ride, that\'s the way you\'ll do it...<br /><br />So, it\'s all about offering you the possibilities. <br /><br />If you are an individual only using the website and email alerts: it\'s free . If you wish to use SMS alerts, you can buy one of the <a href="http://www.car-pooling.be/costs">SMS packages</a>.<br /><br />And if you are a company and wish to integrate the application to your site, you can get a <a href="http://www.car-pooling.be/enterprises">Specific License</a>.<br /><br />Voil\xc3\xa0. It\'s up to you.<br /><br />Happy car-pooling, and Safe Route...", "updated": "2009-11-06T00:26:35.043-08:00", "title": "philosophy", "comments": [], "blog": "5936136819991781356", "tag": "blogger.com", "year": "1999", "id": "2596155641849338248", "categories": "philosophy'}], "tag": "blogger.com", "user": "805854382143", "year": "1999", "id": "5936136819991781356", "categories": ['philosophy']}, {"name": "molhokwai-shadowwork", "title": "shadow work...", "posts": [{"content": "It is just a reflection of your self...<br />So it\'s all just about what you give out...<br /><br />...<br /><br />Right now, I feel like destruction... The lack of Love in this world is deep... deeply deeply rooted... and I simply have to become all Love to let each one acknowledge this... acknowledge, understan